My apologies to my friends on this site, to Marc Weiss, and POV, our hosts. My above post was uncalled for. At best I should have posted it in the darkest corner of the parking lot threat out back.  Instead I got hooked and flamed.<br><br>
I have decided that communication with Mr. Ramon and Mr Barela is simply impossible, as they seem to just wish to<br>
call names, hurl insults, and see their name in print. I wish not to feed into that immaturity, hence I will ignore them entirely from this point out.  I know they will see this as some form of capitulation, or some other nonsensical belief in the superiority of their position (whatever that may be). That is their choice.  I for one believe that I have contributed, with them, to cheapening this site, and I wish to apologize to all, and at least stop my contribution to that cheapening.  <br><br>
